commit_list.message: Add streamed upload. Much more complicated than expected, as S3 does not support chunked transfer, so using setHTTPBodyStream at NSURLConnection level is not possible and we must implement our own HTTP client on top of CoreFoundation. Not really tested in error situations, and probably does not play well with proxies (yet). Implied a bit of reorganization to have abstract S3Operation decorallated from NS-level network classes. Fix #6
